OL,3,CMotor repair shop fined #8,000 for
OL,4,Cfailing to provide clean toilet for
OL,5,Cstaff
OL,7,FA motor repair shop has been sentenced
OL,8,Ffor breaching health and safety
OL,9,Fregulations, after failing to provide
OL,10,Fa clean and suitable toilet and
OL,11,Fwashroom.
OL,13,FThe Health and Safety Executive has
OL,14,Freleased pictures of the toilet at
OL,15,FBrightside Motors Ltd in , which show
OL,16,Fa bin overflowing, mould on the walls
OL,17,Fand an unclean toilet and sink area.
OL,19,FAn inspection in June 2021 found
OL,20,Fwelfare facilities, including the
OL,21,Ftoilet, were in a 'poor state'.
