OL,3,CMotor repair shop fined #8,000 for
OL,4,Cfailing to provide clean toilet for
OL,5,Cstaff
OL,7,FThis included the failure to provide
OL,8,Fsuitable sanitary products and
OL,9,Fadequate washing facilities. There was
OL,10,Fno supply of clean, hot and cold
OL,11,Fwater, no soap nor any toilet paper. A
OL,12,Fletter was then sent by HSE to the
OL,13,Fcompany outlining its health and
OL,14,Fsafety breaches.
OL,16,FFollowing the inspection of the site
OL,17,Fon Holywell Road, HSE served the firm
OL,18,Fwith an Improvements Notices that
OL,19,Frequired them to provide suitable
OL,20,Ftoilets and washing facilities for its
OL,21,Fworkers.
