OL,3,CMotor repair shop fined #8,000 for
OL,4,Cfailing to provide clean toilet for
OL,5,Cstaff
OL,7,FIn December 2021, HSE inspected the
OL,8,Fsite again and found the company had
OL,9,Ftaken no action to address the issues
OL,10,Fwith its welfare facilities.
OL,12,FHSE then served the company with two
OL,13,FImprovement Notices, legally requiring
OL,14,Fthe company to provide suitable
OL,15,Ftoilets and washing facilities,
OL,16,Fincluding hot and cold running water
OL,17,Ffor its staff.
