OL,3,CMotor repair shop fined #8,000 for
OL,4,Cfailing to provide clean toilet for
OL,5,Cstaff
OL,7,FThe company failed to take appropriate
OL,8,Faction to comply with these notices.
OL,9,FDespite being given additional time by
OL,10,FHSE, the company failed to meet the
OL,11,Fdeadline in January 2023.
OL,13,FBrightside Motors Ltd, of Holywell
OL,14,FRoad, Sheffield, pleaded guilty to
OL,15,Fbreaching Section 33(1)(g) of the
OL,16,FHealth and Safety at Work etc Act 1974.
OL,18,FThe company was fined #8,000 and
OL,19,Fordered to pay #3,292.77 in costs at
OL,20,FSheffield Magistrates' Court on 24
OL,21,FJanuary 2024.
